profile: Homesteads Helpers does weekly, bi-weekly, monthly or a one time clean. We also do move in/outs. All staff have a RCMP criminal record checks. They also have a safety check to insure they can work with the elderly and children. We use environmentally friendly supplies. We also have vacuum cleaners if you do not. We also do errands. We have great references. We are insured. We are pet friendly. We provide a free estimate and can meet with you first to discuss your needs. DVA welcome. Seniors discounts. Customer service is our top priority. Office hours are Monday to Saturday 8:00am to 8:00pm. Call 604-316-1363
